		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="dablink">This article is about a general rise in the level of prices.  For the expansion of the early universe, see <a href="/wiki/Inflation_(cosmology)" title="Inflation (cosmology)">Inflation (cosmology)</a>.  For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Inflation_(disambiguation)" title="Inflation (disambiguation)">Inflation (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
